data.description: Perfect Location, fabulous floor plan!! You will love this Four Bedroom Two and a Half bath home with Brand New Plumbing throughout, New Fixtures and Hot Water Heater. In addition to the Four Bedrooms you have a Huge Loft / Bonus area perfect for an office or sitting area. The Kitchen has been upgraded with rich Wood Finish cabinets and Granite counter tops.  The family room has a Fireplace and elegant built-ins. The Master Bedroom is extremely spacious with mirror wardrobes and a well appointed Master bath. Area residents have access to the Sun & Sail Club. There are a huge selection of activities including pickleball, a pool, spa, sauna, barbecue facilities, tennis courts, a clubhouse, and a billiard room. This is the perfect home for relaxing and entertaining with friends and family. For more information Google "Lake Forest Sun and Sail Club"
